\*[SUP]43\*[SUPX]Then shall the righteous shine forth as the sun in the kingdom of their Father. Who hath ears to hear, let him hear.
\*[SUP]44\*[SUPX]Again, the kingdom of heaven is like unto treasure hid in a field; the which when a man hath found, he hideth, and for joy thereof goeth and selleth all that he hath, and buyeth that field.
