\*[SUP]50\*[SUPX]And shall cast them into the furnace of fire: there shall be wailing and gnashing of teeth.
\*[SUP]51\*[SUPX]Jesus saith unto them, Have ye understood all these things? They say unto him, Yea, Lord.
\*[SUP]52\*[SUPX]Then said he unto them, Therefore every scribe which is instructed unto the kingdom of heaven is like unto a man that is an householder, which bringeth forth out of his treasure things new and old.
\*[SUP]53\*[SUPX]And it came to pass, that when Jesus had finished these parables, he departed thence.
