fter these things Paul departed from Athens, and came to Corinth;
\*[SUP]2\*[SUPX]And found a certain Jew named Aquila, born in Pontus, lately come from Italy, with his wife Priscilla; (because that Claudius had commanded all Jews to depart from Rome:) and came unto them.
