nd it came to pass, that, while Apollos was at Corinth, Paul having passed through the upper coasts came to Ephesus: and finding certain disciples,
\*[SUP]2\*[SUPX]He said unto them, Have ye received the Holy Ghost since ye believed? And they said unto him, We have not so much as heard whether there be any Holy Ghost.
\*[SUP]3\*[SUPX]And he said unto them, Unto what then were ye baptized? And they said, Unto John's baptism.
