\*[SUP]17\*[SUPX]And from Miletus he sent to Ephesus, and called the elders of the church.
\*[SUP]18\*[SUPX]And when they were come to him, he said unto them, Ye know, from the first day that I came into Asia, after what manner I have been with you at all seasons,
