\*[SUP]9\*[SUPX]Tribulation and anguish, upon every soul of man that doeth evil, of the Jew first, and also of the Gentile;
\*[SUP]10\*[SUPX]But glory, honour, and peace, to every man that worketh good, to the Jew first, and also to the Gentile:
