\*[SUP]15\*[SUPX]Meditate upon these things; give thyself wholly to them; that thy profiting may appear to all.
\*[SUP]16\*[SUPX]Take heed unto thyself, and unto the doctrine; continue in them: for in doing this thou shalt both save thyself, and them that hear thee.
